title: They Stole my Grandmother's car! with Jon Rudnitsky | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 66
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The babes are joined by comedian Jon Rudnitsky! They talk self car, SNL lifestyle, and much more!!!! THURSDAYS ARE FOR THE BABES!!!
